title: Spanish Winemaker Obtains Permission to Cut Down 154 Acres of California Redwoods
subtitle: Rumor: A Spanish winemaker is planning on cutting down 150 acres of California Redwoods in order to expand their grape growing area.
author: David Mikkelson
vclaim: Artesa Vineyards and Winery is planning to cut down 154 acres of California Redwoods in order to expand their grape growing area.
